Avoid hazards and jump on the enemies to defeat them, and collect all the food!
Face 30 different levels, find all the food and eat it all!
Instructions: WASD or ARROW KEYS to MOVE and JUMP
Key Features:
- 30 Levels
- Easy to learn hard to master
- A lot of different moves to help you to complete the game

Title: Idle Lumber Hero
Description: Tap and move the mouse to move the player! Follow the path of wood and chop down as many as you can! Sell the wood to the market and buy new upgrades to speed up your wood chopping process.
Instructions: Tap and move the mouse to move the player!
Key Features:
- Easy to play
- Click and move mouse to move player

Title: Vegetables Match 3
Description: Swap blocks in order to make a group of 3 or more identical flowers adjacent horizontally or vertically.  Keep matching till you unlock and clear all the tiles. Use power-ups to speed up the process.  There is 36 interesting levels in this game.
Instructions: Use mouse or touchscreen to play this game.

Title: Kaiten Sushi
Description: Help the most  bumbling incompetent sushi chef in the world to prepare his nigiris. Touch the right button for each fish on the screen and show the world how good is your sushi!
Instructions: touch the right icon at the right time
Key Features:
-prerendered graphics
-funny animations

Title: Brick Game 3D
Description: Brick Block, one of the most popular games, is here! Destroy the blocks and go to the next level. Increase your number of balls by having bonuses and pass the levels faster.
Instructions: LEFT and RIGHT ARROW KEYS

Title: Random Cards Tower Defense
Description:
Random Cards: Tower Defense is not an easy game. But you should not be afraid. Consider it a challenge! Consider that you need to become a champion.
Assemble a team of the strongest or smash the enemy one-on-one. Keep in mind that in order to win, you will need to calculate all the actions. Every step must be thought out. Play out different tower defense scenarios, make wise decisions, improve cards. And be prepared for the fact that you will have to make difficult decisions!
Each card has its own strength and its own power. The outcome of the battle will not depend only on chance.
Instructions: Control: left mouse button / touch on an object on the screen of a mobile device
Key Features:
⚔️ Upgrade battle cards and hero abilities.
⚔️ Collect cups and collect rewards in regular weekly events, in VIP PASS, open chests, get gold, diamonds, new cards and heroes.
⚔️ Each new card has its own unique ability.
⚔️ Collect your unique deck to defend the tower.

Title: Spooky Bubble Shooter
Description: It is a spooky bubble shooter game; collect the Golden 'Jack-o'-lanterns' hidden among the zombie's eyes. There will be 72 challenging levels.  In each level you will find a different challenge with 'different type of items and power ups'. To complete a level you must collect all the 'Jack-o'-lanterns'. Shoot the eye on the board to make groups of 3 or more eyes of the same color. You must complete a level within allowed time. You will get better score if you complete the level early.
Instructions: Aim the arrow and shoot the item towards it's identical to make a group of 3 or more similar items.

Title: Fruit Merge Reloaded
Description: Dive into the juicy and colorful world of Fruit Merge Reloaded, a captivating merging game that combines the addictive gameplay of 2048 with the sweetness of your favorite fruits! Your task is to merge identical fruits to create new and exotic varieties, aiming to reach the ultimate fruit fusion.
Instructions: Touch and move

Title: Hidden Candies
Description:
Hidden Candies is an skill based hidden object game where you need to tap all the hidden candies in a level. 
You need to complete 16 challenging levels to win this game.
Instructions: Use mouse or touch pad to find hidden objects.

Title: Jump The Wall
Description: Jump The Wall is a fun jumping game. You need to jump over heavy walls and if you hit an obstacle or fall, then you will faint for a while. The time has come to test your reflexes, share it with your friends. Surpass the other opponents and become the ultimate winner!
Instructions: Hold to move, release to shoot
Key Features:
- Interesting gameplay in the genre!
- Beautiful & colorful graphics!
- Intuitive interface!
- Easy controls!

Title: Insect Pic Puzzles
Description: Move pieces of insect images between tiles to arrange them in proper order. Touch or click a block to shift it to an adjacent blank place. You will lose points after each second, so finish it in a smart way to save maximum points.
Instructions: Use a mouse or touchpad to play this game.

Title: Jewel Halloween
Description: Use your sharpness and logic in the new Halloween game. Enjoy the adventure full of pumpkins, monsters, and skeletons while collecting coins. Can you beat all the levels without getting scared?
Instructions: You have to match at least three items as sharply as possible. By matching at least four items, you can get more points and useful boosters like bombs. If you need a little help, try spinning the lucky wheel. Collect as many coins as you can and become the king of the spooky season.
Key Features:
300 levels
Halloween scary theme
6 different boosters
Events: Lucky wheel, shop, surprise box

Title: Soccer Maze
Description: In front of you, there is a ball, a maze, and an opponent. If you can quickly analyze the maze and navigate the ball through the correct path to the opposing goal, you will defeat your opponent. Show your skills!
Instructions: 1.Player(Left And Right Arrow Keys, Enter) - 2.Player(A, D, Space)
Key Features: 2D, Single Player And Two Player, 10 Levels, Different Ball Styles

Title: C Virus Game: Outbreak
Description: The new virus hit the earth, it is C-virus! More than 90% of the population is infected. You are ex-marine with PTSD, make your way to escape and stay alive!
Instructions:
WASD or arrow keys to walk 
Left mouse button to attack/shoot 
Right mouse button to aim 
F to interact with objects 
Left shift to run 
Left Ctrl to crouch 
Space bar to jump

Title: Strike It!
Description: A cool game where you need to shoot down all the little men so that they fly in different directions! Bright locations and a lot of challenging tasks are waiting for you! Show accuracy and foresight: everything depends on the trajectory of the blow!
Instructions:
Aim the ball at the target and release your finger. Just watch the ball bounce and drop people to the ground. A bowling battle simulator without the Internet is waiting for you. Hit the strike and get more coins to buy new balls.
PC control: hold down the left mouse button on the ball and guide the ball. Let go - the ball will fly.
Control on mobile devices: hold your finger on the screen on the ball and guide the ball. Let go and the ball will fly.
Key Features:
Dodgeball: Scatter Everyone With a Ball is a free 3D game where you need to hit the ball so that all the little men on the field fly apart. Don't think that it will be as easy as just knocking down cans. Be precise as if you are playing 3D bowling. Knock out the strike and watch the enemies fly away.

An exciting game with real physics: the little men fly in different directions from the impact of the ball!
P.S. No one was hurt!

Title: Easter Link
Description: "Easter Link" is a Mahjong linking game where your goal is to match two identical blocks. The connecting line between two matching blocks can have only two turns. Test your skills in this unique twist on the classic board game by making connections between matching tiles. Race against the clock as you strive to clear the board before time runs out. Are you up for the challenge?
Instructions: Use mouse or touch pad to play this game.

Title: Tiles Hop Ball Master
Description: Tiles Hop Ball Master is a ball jumping skillful arcade game. With 3D platforms and a white ball, you are supposed to control the real-time position of the ball to arrive at the top of the platforms at each level. While the ball is jumping on the platforms automatically, you could also collect some gold coins for more scores. Good luck and have a good time!
Instructions: Drag to play.

Title: Bubble Shooter Valentines
Description: Bubble Shooter Valentines is a Classical bubble shooter game, with Modern features and valentines theme. Heart Balloons are coming to you; collect them before they reach to you. Use power-ups to overcome the challenges.
Instructions: Use touchscreen or mouse to play this bubble shooter game

Title: Squid Survival
Description:
Squid Game

Play the squid game

Run and stop! Win squid game or lose.
Green light - move, red light - stay.

If you get noticed you are excluded from the game.

This is a real game where challenges await you.

Join the most dangerous game and become the winner
and remember you drive quieter - you will continue
Instructions:
Touch control on devices with touchscreens. Mouse control on PC.
Follow the instructions that will be in the game.
Key Features:
Green light - Red light. Run and stop! Win or lose and lose everything. Green light - move
Red light - stop, If you are noticed you are excluded from the game. Join the most dangerous game and become a winner
and remember you drive quieter - you will continue

Title: Celebrity Ari All Around The Fashion
Description: Welcome to Celebrity Ari All Around The Fashion. Celebrity Ari plans to try different fashion trends. She needs some help to choose the perfect costumes and outfits. Browse her wardrobe and choose the perfect outfits for each fashion trend. Play and have fun with this new game!
Instructions: Left Mouse Button Click

Title: Running Bot
Description:
Control your robot to avoid the obstacles (trees and rocks), collect the Xmas gifts to upgrade the powerup items and the robot's health. Pick up the powerup items (shields, magnets, and magical wings) for more advantages. Keep running as far as you can, to create your new high scores and raise your name on the leaderboard.
Are you ready for the challenges? Play now!
Instructions:
Mobile:
- Swipe left or right to move
- Swipe up to jump

Desktop:
- Press left or right arrow keys to move
- Press up arrow key to jump
- Press Space bar to replay the game
Key Features:
3D
High resolution

Title: RESOLVE a math game
Description:
If you like math, or not... you will definitively love RESOLVE, the best math game ever. It is a fun game, it is quick and easy to play, and it is also challenging for everyone.

At the bottom of the screen you can see unfilled equations. The solution is on the top of the screen. Just link the correct numbers together so you can complete the equation.
 
Easy, isn't it? Really? Well play RESOLVE now and find if you are a true math genius.
Instructions: link the correct numbers together so you can complete the equation
Key Features:
+ Daily challenge
+ 3000 levels
+ than 30 packs
+ Achievement

Title: Frosty Connection Quest
Description: Join us on a frosty adventure with "Frosty Connection Quest," an exhilarating online matching puzzle game meticulously crafted to be super fun for both kids and adults alike. "Frosty Connection Quest" online playground where the whimsy of winter meets the thrill of puzzle-solving. Have fun playing!
Instructions: Click or tap two tiles with a clear path between them with no more than two turns.

Title: Imposter Killer
Description: You need to quickly find the impostors and kill them. Do not appear within sight of your replacement, or your life will be in danger! Don't forget to use gold to buy new characters and enhance your personal abilities!
Instructions: Swipe to play.

Title: Jelly Quest Mania
Description: Collect the jellies in this free and fun match-3 puzzle game. Whenever you want to pass time, this game can provide the right experience thanks to the cool gameplay.
Instructions: In this game, you can play and match three or more jellies of the same type to collect them. Complete all the objectives before you run out of time or moves. In each level, you are playing against limited time and moves. Some jellies are locked, free them by making a match.
Key Features:
Challenging match-3
50 diverse levels
Uplifting graphics

Title: ColorPoly
Description:
Color Poly is one of the simple and addicting color matching puzzle game.
The objective is simple to match falleningcolor bars with the rotating color square.
Instructions:
-Tap on the Play Button.
-Tap on the screen to rotate the square.

Title: Loop Master
Description:
Loop-Master is a fun way of increasing your logic skills.
It can be considered a puzzle game and logic game, about creating intricate looping patterns, or just the application of using a simple concept: connecting multiple things and making fun of it.
Loop-Master has more than 30+ levels and is a game for anxiety. Also, it is a tap-and-relax game that increases your logic.
Instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

Title: Scythe death blow
Description:
Launch a death scythe at enemies. All monsters will die in one hit, but you must kill them in 20 seconds. Use the skills and obstacles of the map for a successful game.

*This game was inspired by: 20 SECOND GAME JAM
Instructions: Easy control with a mouse or touch screen. The weapon flies in the direction of your click.
Key Features: Scythe, only mouse, endless, one hit kill, pixel art, retro

Title: Fantasy Triple Mahjong
Description: A triple mahjong game with Fantasy theme. You can eliminate only three of same tiles. Those tiles can be selected which have at least 2 adjacent sides open. Take as less time as possible to get more score.
Instructions: Use mouse or touch pad to play this game.

Title: Realistic Wheelbarrow
Description: Think of a mountain and a wheelbarrow and a track with challenging obstacles, you should be able to climb that mountain with the wheelbarrow so balanced that you can reach the destination and enjoy the view!
Instructions: Arrow Keys, W A S D Keys And Touch Screen With Mouse
Key Features: 3d, singleplayer, a wheelbarrow, a mountain and a rough road

Title: Animal Jump
Description:
Become the winner of the race for survival!

AJ, it's a ranger mechanic game with fun elements and simple controls!
Collect gold, use boosts and finish first!
Instructions:
Simple controls: start on the space bar, control the main character with arrows, wad or mouse.

Dodge obstacles, collect gold, upgrade your hero and win the race for survival.
Key Features:
Compete with other players and take only first places!

A variety of locations, a large selection of characters and cool races!

Fun runner with booster boosts and your starting speed)

Title: Pop It Fidget 3D
Description: I have to say, it is very relaxing for people to squeeze out the bubble wraps. Pop It Fidget 3D is a relaxation arcade game with 3D different shapes of bubbles. There are three types of patterns with 3D bubbles. When you squeeze all the bubbles of a pattern, it will turn over 180 degrees for you to play unlimited times. Have a rest without any mind!
Instructions: Tap to hit the bubbles
Key Features: 3 types of patterns

Title: Idle Pinball Breakout
Description:
Welcome to Idle Pinball Breakout: A unique mix of pinball arcade physics + brick breaker + idle offline earning.

- Realistic physics-based simulation (based on box2d)
- Upgrade balls and tweak each ball's physics
- Upgrade launcher and other gameplay features
- Earn gold even when you are offline
- Unique boosters to make your own gameplay: you can automate, boost earnings, adjust gameplays and extend offline earnings
- No microtransaction, no forced ads, only optional ads with massive in-game rewards
Instructions: Explained in-game
Key Features:
- Realistic physics-based simulation (based on box2d)
- Upgrade balls and tweak each ball's physics
- Upgrade launcher and other gameplay features
- Earn gold even when you are offline
- Unique boosters to make your own gameplay: you can automate, boost earnings, adjust gameplays and extend offline earnings
- No microtransaction, no forced ads, only optional ads with massive in-game rewards

Title: Star Maze
Description: Star Maze is a challenging Maze game with 100 levels. Paint your way through a maze in this beautiful puzzle game! Move through the maze to color your tiles and collect all the stars.
Instructions: Swipe to move the ball and collect the stars.

Title: Pixel Hardcore
Description: Pixel Journey is a platformer game. To complete the level, you need to find the key, and then head to the door. It seems simple, but various obstacles will be waiting for you on the way. Will you be able to overcome them all?
Instructions: Control is available on a computer and a mobile device . On a computer, use the WASD keys to control the character, on a mobile device, use the on-screen buttons.

Title: Parmesan Partisan Deluxe
Description: You are the last defense, you are a lonely cheesy partisan who has to protect his people from the menace of the Mice People, who wants to conquer an eat all the cheese they can find! You are the last hope of your people: defend them with your shotgun, kill as many rats as you can, and free your nation from the rodents conquerors!
Instructions:
WASD and ARROWS to Move
Right Mouse Button to Dodge
Left Button to Shoot
Key Features:
- 10 different levels
- 5 angry mice with different weapons
- 9 different weapons to choose from

Title: Gangs Idle City
Description: Gangs Idle City game is a fun simple gangster arcade idle game. You use a funny gangster character in the game and try to earn money in various ways. You continue the game by improving the tools you use step by step and expanding your environment. As the levels pass, things will grow more skillfully, try to control the city.
Instructions:
MOVE: "W,A,S,D" or "ARROW KEYS"   
JUMP: "SPACE"   
DASH: "SHIFT"
